Dev stub grants instantly via `WG.State.grantEnergy('iap-refill')`. Apple/Google/Stripe channels untouched.

## Where energy is shown in UI

- **Top strip** (`#top-strip` in `index.html`): amber chip `⚡ <cur>/<max>` with "+1 in MM:SS" countdown row beneath. Switches to "FULL" at cap.
- **Energy Modal** (`#energy-modal`, `js/meta/meta-energy-modal.js`): opens on chip tap or out-of-energy interrupt. Header current/max + countdown, watch-ad row, 5-row refill ladder with BEST VALUE badge on refill_30.
- **Results screen** (`js/hunt/hunt-results.js`): two new reward rows — `⚡ +3` (win refund) and `⚡ +10 First Clear!`.
- **Toasts** (top-center): `+20 ⚡ Daily Login (Day N)`, then 600ms later `+50 ⚡ 7-Day Streak!` on Day 7.
- **Chest loot reveal**: `HuntFXNumbers.spawn` floats text upward from chest world position; matching top-strip chip pulses 600ms.

## Happy-path test results

Browser smoke at `http://localhost:3996/`:

1. ✅ Cold load with cleared `wg_save_v2` → energy chip renders 30/30 (Day 1 +20 capped at MAX), "FULL" countdown.
2. ✅ Backdate `lastRegenAt` 32 min → `processEnergyRegen` granted 2 (offline catch-up); anchor advanced 30 min, 2 min leftover preserved.
3. ✅ `startHunt(1, 'day')` with energy=30 → -5 deducted, runtime built. With energy=2 → modal opened, no deduction.
4. ✅ `HuntResults.show({ cleared: true, energyRefund: 3 })` → row "⚡ +3" present. With `firstClearBonus: 10` → row "⚡ +10 First Clear!" present. `cleared:false` → no ⚡ rows.
5. ✅ Treasure chest spawnChest + tick → state transitions closed→opening→loot grant; chest removed; `chest:opened` event fired with kind/amount/guaranteed.
6. ✅ 1000 unforced rolls → 502 gold / 264 energy / 157 fragment / 58 rare_mat / 19 gem (within tolerance).
7. ✅ 500 forced rolls (5th-chest streak) → 467 energy + 33 gem = 500/500 guaranteeable (no leak).
8. ✅ 5 sequential chest opens → 5th has `guaranteed:true`, lands on energy.
9. ✅ Energy chip click → modal opens with "ENERGY" title; out-of-energy reason → "OUT OF ENERGY" red title.
10. ✅ refill_5 dev-stub purchase → energy 4→9; BEST VALUE badge anchored on refill_30.
11. ✅ Watch-ad rewarded video flow grants +5 ⚡ on success; daily-cap remaining shown in modal.
12. ✅ Daily-login matrix: cold start grants Day 1 +20; yesterday→today returns streak 2; same-day call no-op (returns 0); 1970-gap resets to 1; streak=6 + yesterday triggers Day 7 bonus event {bonus:50}, both toasts visible, streak wraps to 0.
13. ✅ wasFirstClear sampling: `bestWaves[3] === undefined` → true; `=== 0` → false; `=== 1.2` → false.

No console errors across all flows.

