Notes for the next worker (Missions Pass / Whale Ladder / Sub Blockers):
- `WG.State.grantEnergy(amount, reason)` is the single grant path — emits `energy:change` and respects MAX.
- `WG.State.spendEnergy(amount)` returns false when below cost (callers must handle UI gate).
- `state.forge.rareMats` is the new lazy field for chest rare-mat drops; downstream forge work can read it.
- `WG.EnergyModal.open({ reason: 'out-of-energy' })` is the standard interrupt; same modal serves voluntary refills.
